Creating (Declaring) a Relation
▪ Simplest form is:
CREATE TABLE <name> (
<list of elements>
);
▪ To delete a relation: 
DROP TABLE <name>;

57
Deletion
▪ To delete tuples satisfying a condition 
from some relation:
DELETE FROM <relation> 
WHERE <condition>;

